      {
        "title": "Input Form",
        "description": "<div>\n<div>This form will capture the outcomes of your initial conversation with the HR or business leader sponsoring the program. It is designed to structure key insights from the discussion and make them available for use in the broader Client Impact Measurement process.</div>\n<div></div>\n<div>Your responses to these five core questions will create a consistent foundation for measuring program effectiveness and aligning success criteria across engagements.</div>\n<div></div>\n<div><strong>This is not a diagnostic tool—it’s a way to document what matters most to the client and inform meaningful follow-up. </strong>This form simply ensures we <strong>capture the essentials in a structured, shareable way</strong>.</div>\n</div>",
